name: The Rani Garden Bed & Breakfast
address: Jl. Pulau Moyo IV No.2, Pedungan, Denpasar Selatan, Kota Denpasar, Bali 80222, Indonesia
review 1: Aweosme vibe at night, great services and well prepared breakfast. either you are a local or international tourist this place is a recommended place to stay
review 2: Our first hotel in Bali and we loved it! The breakfast is also good and the pool is clean.
review 3:
Currently the condition of the hotel very bad.
No staf, dirty bed and quit,
No  mat in the front of bath room, no bath room amenities, only toliet tissue.
Night lamp broken.
Sorry to say..ror current situation is not recomended hotel.
review 4: Very helpful stuff, great place to stay. There are a few shops and warungs near hotel,you can try local food if you want) and you can find a fruit shop near hotel. Room are very clean, with good bed and fridge. Hotel style i think - environment style, at the room most furniture are from wood. I like it!
review 5: Great B&B in Denpasar. Very quiet place with friendly accommodating staff just outside the busy city center. Rooms were roomy with a personal fridge, small kitchen and nice bathroom. The shower uses a small boiler-system so multiple hot showers are not possible back to back. Overall a nice and peaceful experience.
